Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱惑…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼地…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼时…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与彼人的维系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否陪我一下呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自白…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且坚韧而又温情地联系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次还是待在家里休息比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己想要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁绊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触碰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维系…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联结…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小全和小多不能到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们只能送你到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…那个人…就会来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百…目鬼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到了侑子小姐打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我去她那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是让我去接你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再继续这样下去就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是指会死掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你见了那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…她并没有对我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有觉得不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你就没有想到其他什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不也说  最近很少受到魑魅魍魉的影响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有其他什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…她不是个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是否是人类  你还并不清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算…是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经和她约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在公园见面…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿  我们来打个赌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日到底会不会去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用赌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是四月一日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有的  只是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学没带便当来还真是少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  已经好久没做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你脸色不怎么太好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像上次晕倒的那天也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是白色情人节的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}（白色情人节：女生在2月14日情人节时会送礼物或巧克力给心仪的男孩，\N等到3月14日时男生若也对此女孩有所感觉，就会回礼予这位女孩。）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉这是买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象是在西方公园的附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然其实我是想自己来做  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是百目鬼同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日会去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮百目鬼同学加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…我想是不会去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉强自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还能再见到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再见面了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要再见面了比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我说了什么失礼的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是因为我的身体的缘故  请不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「总是觉得很寂寞！」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是这样说过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能让她觉得更寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不冷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明叫你不要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知道来见我的话  会让自己更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  别人也告诉过我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是这样  那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要是你觉得寂寞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…会感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百…目鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不管我说什么  你都会来见她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经  不再寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有你在一起  我已经不会再感到寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有人需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想要失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要射？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为她不是人类吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做了个选择而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经顺利地  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那边就算是不顺利也不会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:16:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象最近我总是这个样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我来的人  是百目鬼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  没有听你的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  因为那是四月一日的选择呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算明知见她会有危险  你还是要去见她对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我之前所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人可以有任何愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福的也好  不幸福的也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么样的选择  只要是自己的选择就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要四月一日自己不后悔的话  那就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼也是…做出了选择
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使射杀了那个女人会伤害到四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使会被四月一日怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是不希望四月一日消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以四月一日只要再做个选择就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择今后要如何对待百目鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道那个女人是什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她不是人类  对我来说她一样是个温柔而又亲切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我来告诉你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人在消失之前说的话  是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下打工费又要增加了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  明天一定能恢复健康的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天也好好地休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了那么长时间的差  也很累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在主人的床上薰上香才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要准备好睡前酒才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吵醒四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地  悄悄地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地  悄悄地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地  悄悄地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个好梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小～葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了便当
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主题是春天！久违的便当很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵才棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待午饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是搭了小葵的顺风车哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有豆皮寿司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你老是要吃豆皮寿司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是三色饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  没办法  将就下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么口气啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系真好呢  四月一日同学和百目鬼同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的三色饭团中放鲑鱼了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么你还要有选择吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有梅子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有！可是一样很美味啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是找侑子小姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请往这边
