Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上没有偶然
