Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我之间的相遇是有意义的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铭刻于心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻阅记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.21,0:23:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔遥远而持续着的故事的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定  还相信着会再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:23:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知是在何时…
